latestIgtvVideos.caption:
🌟 40 MIN plank workout BELOW🌟 Didn’t plan to buy the same sports bra but great minds think alike even in the fitness realm 😂😂 @vinitamungi had me do a plank variation workout today which looked a bit like this: 30 seconds each- 
💫 Plank 💫 Plank Jacks 💫 Side Plank 💫 Plank crawl 💫 Bear to Plank 💫 Plank shoulder taps…. 
Brutal but what a core burn out!! Try it - anytime you’re free. And since the workout changes every 30 seconds you won’t even realize that you finish 40 MINUTES of planks!!
.
.
.
